## Limitations
The findings are based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of technological advancements in nursing. Additionally, the rapid pace of technological change means that some information may become outdated quickly. Further research and continuous updates are necessary to maintain a comprehensive understanding of the impact of technology on nursing.